sanam teri kasam is a 1982 indian hindi romantic drama film directed by k. s. burman and produced by &lt;unk&gt; khan . the film stars ajay dev , kulbhushan kharbanda , kulbhushan kharbanda and kulbhushan kharbanda in lead roles . the film had musical score by r. d. burman . the film was a remake of tamil film sanam teri kasam .